{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"49da1def85","title":"讽刺诗——老爷腔调","origin":"中共中央高级党校 校部办公室编印《整风学习讨论问题参考资料》第7期，1957年8月8日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6682b8a3af","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":22,"articleId":"49da1def85"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"3841bd11a6","name":"宋宏钊"},{"id":"3aae6e8366","name":"中共中央高级党校"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e59a1c5a92","type":"title","text":"讽刺诗——老爷腔调","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"71184ce84e","type":"authors","text":"中共中央高级党校宋宏钊","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"b2fe212620","type":"subtitle","text":"（宋宏钊：师资训练部第六班哲学专业第三支部学员，入学前陕西省委党校总路綫教研组副组长）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"64f3e85871","type":"subtitle","text":"老爷腔调——模拟一个官僚主义者的自我批评","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"434f76ad62","type":"paragraph","text":"“大家提的意见我十分欢迎，","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"a51bbc6c08","type":"paragraph","text":"现在让我来作自我批评，","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"0858f64f7c","type":"paragraph","text":"但是其中还有几点，","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"61cc2367a5","type":"paragraph","text":"我必须作个简略的说明。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"aeee97b398","type":"paragraph","text":"“大家批评我这幅严肃面孔，","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"e68813cdfe","type":"paragraph","text":"有人甚至说我冷酷无情，","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"ba798148c7","type":"paragraph","text":"岂知身居领导地位，","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"0031332e4c","type":"paragraph","text":"也有些难以告人的苦衷。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"5372b13cd4","type":"paragraph","text":"经常碰到些辣手问题，","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"c3b3f0b4c1","type":"paragraph","text":"日常事务也纠缠不清，","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"226615fc07","type":"paragraph","text":"永远得不到半点轻松，","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"6f6e1acaf4","type":"paragraph","text":"因此不自觉的就板起面孔。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"8b631a2ade","type":"paragraph","text":"“和同志谈话的时候，","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"8f4aed2a5d","type":"paragraph","text":"我承认有些简单作风，","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"032c5b0e13","type":"paragraph","text":"不同意就把头摆几摆，","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"bb68cd0f14","type":"paragraph","text":"同意时就鼻子哼一哼，","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"dd0ce53545","type":"paragraph","text":"我认为这样就能表达意见，","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"ca03ded300","type":"paragraph","text":"何必要啰啰索索作过多的说明。","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"9e93319052","type":"paragraph","text":"根据这就批评我麻木不仁，","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"7da1740395","type":"paragraph","text":"我觉得这字眼下得似乎太重。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"45638a724d","type":"paragraph","text":"“有人批评我缺乏民主作风，","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"9f8d37aeb8","type":"paragraph","text":"这简直等于捕风捉影，","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"a1330a67cc","type":"paragraph","text":"我有十几年的革命锻炼，","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"1dde5c7c1d","type":"paragraph","text":"从来也没有独断专行，","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"25f62fcb3a","type":"paragraph","text":"我从来尊重合理的意见，","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"b249f9b3e3","type":"paragraph","text":"我从来接受正确的批评。","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"200c52710c","type":"paragraph","text":"但提意见也得有个原则，","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"9c0290b7b9","type":"paragraph","text":"有些人专门‘吹毛求疵’‘中伤领导’，","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"ab439df623","type":"paragraph","text":"有些人专门‘无中生有’‘鼓浪兴风’。","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"e21d1d7ed2","type":"paragraph","text":"如果像这样滥用民主，","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"e78a0e12b9","type":"paragraph","text":"不及时制止如何能行，","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"ab77021d6c","type":"paragraph","text":"须知民主也不是极端民主，","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"adfbefb023","type":"paragraph","text":"还必须要有必要的集中。","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"be7fe3d7d8","type":"paragraph","text":"“有人说我有宗派情绪，","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"f808cd1dea","type":"paragraph","text":"这无疑是别具用心的恶意进攻。","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"5ab1bdb07e","type":"paragraph","text":"要知道：","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"1c9b0d62e9","type":"paragraph","text":"干部的能力有高有低，","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"a1fb3ab31a","type":"paragraph","text":"干部的品质也良莠不等，","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"6b83845edc","type":"paragraph","text":"谁不爱那‘守职尽责，’‘无是无非’的好干部，","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"4ad31d1b68","type":"paragraph","text":"谁不讨厌‘尖嘴长舌’‘爱提意见’的糊涂虫，","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"4cb2cba228","type":"paragraph","text":"我既具有正常的感情，","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"3f56cb4abf","type":"paragraph","text":"当然也是爱恶分明，","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"4aabebd04e","type":"paragraph","text":"好干部很自然的团结到我周围，","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"ea27137909","type":"paragraph","text":"难道这不是合理合情。","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"8a8fdf21d5","type":"paragraph","text":"“有人说我作风粗暴，","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"781e253b68","type":"paragraph","text":"有人说我压制批评，","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"d2a068a675","type":"paragraph","text":"有人说我生活特殊，","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"091e792a9f","type":"paragraph","text":"有人说我不了解下情，","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"8f3704d4f9","type":"paragraph","text":"这些蜚言谤语，","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"4394a2a576","type":"paragraph","text":"原自无关轻重。","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"ae45a69d18","type":"paragraph","text":"有人竟说我是官僚主义，","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"a1e04fde8a","type":"paragraph","text":"这简直是越出范围的恶毒进攻。","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"a64afbfbd1","type":"paragraph","text":"分明是目无领导，","index":56,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"99a165ce22","type":"paragraph","text":"分明是头脑发疯，","index":57,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"b3e1285c1e","type":"paragraph","text":"幸亏我这人宽大为怀，","index":58,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"f0fe8c21a7","type":"paragraph","text":"最多作个严厉的批评，","index":59,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"f12478d6fc","type":"paragraph","text":"如果遇见个狭隘的领导，","index":60,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"54471f0b1f","type":"paragraph","text":"就会把你革命的前途断送。","index":61,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"22a258be6a","type":"paragraph","text":"要知道：","index":62,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"10bb239bae","type":"paragraph","text":"一个干部的一切，","index":63,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"62205bcebc","type":"paragraph","text":"都由领导来操纵，","index":64,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"5de0395c52","type":"paragraph","text":"你如果尊重他","index":65,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"9d80d7b63f","type":"paragraph","text":"他就是个赐福的天官，","index":66,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"017e123d1d","type":"paragraph","text":"你如果得罪他，","index":67,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"c97c15b638","type":"paragraph","text":"他会变成个降祸的灾星。","index":68,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"a62d04c2a6","type":"paragraph","text":"“同志们！","index":69,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"b6675e3b41","type":"paragraph","text":"你们提意见必须十分慎重，","index":70,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"e756dbe9ac","type":"paragraph","text":"你们必须把是非分清。","index":71,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"b4676a700a","type":"paragraph","text":"党既然决定我负责这个单位，","index":72,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"34669f5e70","type":"paragraph","text":"这就说明我有作领导的本领，","index":73,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"72f06e82ce","type":"paragraph","text":"反对我也就等于反对我们的党，","index":74,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"19a5cf6222","type":"paragraph","text":"对我忠诚也就是对党忠诚。”","index":75,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"},{"id":"c898de2c2b","type":"paragraph","text":" 5月22日","index":76,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85"}],"page":{"id":"af9d56174c","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"49da1def85","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}